{"tid":2102893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【記得】大家排隊果陣要提前後左右2樣野！！","createTime":"2020-07-10T23:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T07:28:45.000Z","uid":154486,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"61da8e230d37d98f584779cb300b8ad4ce92e487","tid":2102893,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T23:14:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">變得太快好多銀髮族都可能唔知！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n一、要<span class=\"red\"><strong>帶住址證明</strong></span>，唔可以用網站cap圖<br />\n<br />\n初選協調人之一民主動力於初選前一天發現，使用選舉事務處網站查證選民紀錄的截圖有機會違反香港法例第541A章。<br />\n<br />\n民主動力宣佈<span class=\"red\"><strong>擱置使用任何選民驗證方法</strong></span>，市民參與初選投票時可提供以下其中一項文件：<br />\n👉🏻住址證明（文本、電子版、截圖和相片均接納），如水電煤收費單、銀行月結單等；<br />\n👉🏻過往投票通知書。<br />\n<br />\n二、唔用APP，<strong><span class=\"red\">統一全部人用網站</span></strong><br />\n因為有狗搞局既緣故，不論An機apple機都係上網站做，唔係佢個App做"},{"pid":"594f4845210a5e7d8ceda2ae44800a5a430d0b4f","tid":2102893,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T23:16:40.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91b801d977b01bd6211709e4a5b0d0dd276ad9b","tid":2102893,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T23:16:53.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f0be15b5b7d8082a1655a80ecff015de3417cd","tid":2102893,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T23:17:20.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae916b9584ced455d5d0d2b512ee26acd44b74